<div class="inner" id="msg_733581"><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">目录/Index</span></strong><br><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">INTRODUCTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;2楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 世界观<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;3楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 守护神<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;4楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 出云<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;5楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人物范例<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;6楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 用语集<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;7楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 制作人员名单<br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">PLAYER SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;8楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人物卡模板<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;9楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 个人资料<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;10楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 构筑<br><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;11楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 类别资料<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;12楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 强袭者<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;13楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 传导者<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;14楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 歼灭者<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;15楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 骑士级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;16楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 激突级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;17楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 超级级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;18楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 灾厄级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;19楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 魔幻级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;20楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 同盟级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;21楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 闪电级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;22楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 古强者<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;23楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 守护神特技<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;24楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 泛用特技：人生经历<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;25楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 加护列表</span><br><span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;26楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;27楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：骑士级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;28楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：激突级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;29楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：超级级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;30楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：灾厄级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;31楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：魔幻级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;32楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：同盟级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;33楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：闪电级<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;34楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 物品资料：泛用守护神（米勒斯）&amp;泛用载具<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;35楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 泛用武装<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;36楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 泛用附加组件<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;37楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人类用武装资料&amp;人类用防具资料<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;38楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一般物品资料<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;39楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 生活方式表&amp;住宅表</span><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">WORLD SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;40楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 机甲历0063年<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;41楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 机甲历年表<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;42楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 拉夫帝国与奈落<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;43楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PMC “Fortune”<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;44楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 凰市<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;45楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 国家与组织<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;46楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 人物列表<br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">RULE SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;47楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 行为判定规则<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;48楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 游戏的进行<br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;49楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 战斗规则<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;50楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 战斗规则-方格<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;51楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 攻击与防御<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;52楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 特技</span><br><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;53楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 守护神的运用<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;54楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 守护神的特殊处理（合体&amp;变形）<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;55楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 细则</span><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">GAMEMASTER SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;56楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; GM规则<br><span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color">&nbsp; &nbsp;57楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;58楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：守护神<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;59楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：人类之敌<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;60楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enemy：其他Enemy</span><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">SCENARIO SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;61楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 模组的读法<br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">APPENDIX</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;62楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 资源<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>
