<h5 id="subject_734865">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=77570.msg734865#msg734865" rel="nofollow">Re: 钢之守护神RPG（メタリックガーディアンRPG）-规则书</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_734865'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_734865'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #11 于:</strong> 2015-07-07, 周二 02:43:37 &#187;</div>
