<h5 id="subject_735320">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=77570.msg735320#msg735320" rel="nofollow">Re: 钢之守护神RPG（メタリックガーディアンRPG）-规则书</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_735320'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_735320'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #14 于:</strong> 2015-07-08, 周三 21:37:57 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_735320_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
